{"tid":1385781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給發夢嘅手足-最快disable Touch ID 同 Face ID 嘅方法","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:32:40.000Z","uid":103534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbd86c0af4beab52944740f8a37fc6870292543","tid":1385781,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">iphone 限定功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\niPhone 5-7<br />\n<br />\n打開SOS 功能<br />\n<br />\n响Save screen 時，快速㩒5下 power button.<br />\n<br />\n之後cancel<br />\n<br />\n你就發現要入密碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPD1nqy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPD1nqy.png&h=0e0d2722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIphone 8-X<br />\n<br />\n㩒住power button + volume button <br />\n<br />\n之後cancel <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0j4kdz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0j4kdz.png&h=c0437c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啲狗撚識unlock 你部手機咩，我夠膽講，除左FBI，冇人做到暫時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有用就share 俾你嘅手足！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5920ef5b01b55b63d05e346890371b82256e7a82","tid":1385781,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">穩陣嘅set埋10次錯password就洗機！</span></span>"},{"pid":"24cd43fdf2618c8d8f1bf87832f4f0d958e26e25","tid":1385781,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"d31cd44e321b8317b478b68654791a00